{"tid":757434,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"求助個案—HKBN D 電話人昆左我","createTime":"2018-07-27T00:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T19:48:45.000Z","uid":149562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68b5ca29d0248b43058b97d7c52b386bde4d3c94","tid":757434,"uid":149562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:39:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有一日有個電話打黎，話自己係hkbn 既人，話做D咩問卷調查，咁我個日好得閒就理下佢啦。<br />\n之後完左就話：「多謝你咁支持我地香港寬頻，咁我地送返mytv super 至尊版比你啦。」<br />\n我就話：「送？」<br />\nstaff:「係呀，唔洗錢既。原價月費$98 ，咁依家就送，直至呢份約完。」<br />\n我再問：「真係唔洗錢？免費既？<br />\nStaff「係，免費既，我地6月5號 update 完就自動生效。」<br />\n咁我就話好啦幫我攪啦。<br />\n<br />\n點知，我今日交錢發現，佢收我5/6-30/6 同 1/7-30/7 的$98月費。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打，我可以點做？<br />\n利申：錢已交只求cut 左之後個垃圾！"},{"pid":"254f33d0b60fdd47ade130f7b4a19e0fb0c473ef","tid":757434,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"打上去屌柒佢啦"},{"pid":"18f2bb78d9861d461feef4916e7fd989971c6dc6","tid":757434,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"錢已交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee50b23d3ae2757117d57bf33566026fac3c0325","tid":757434,"uid":24712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}